    "description": "<p>Moderate&nbsp;<em>search&nbsp;</em>or Difficult&nbsp;<em>Perception&nbsp;</em>check to determine the weapon's true nature.</p>\n<p>Lightfoils&nbsp;were a type of small&nbsp;lightsaber&nbsp;that boasted a one-handed hilt and generated a slim&nbsp;plasma&nbsp;blade.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Game Notes:&nbsp;</strong>On a roll of 1 on the wild die, the beam flickers and fades. Repairing the weapon takes two hours and a Moderate lightsaber repair roll.</p>\n<p><strong>Developer's note:&nbsp;</strong>The user's melee strength modifier is automaticaly added is added to lightfoil damage rolls. To make life easier, the lightfoil is coded to grant&nbsp;<strong>STR+1D+2</strong>&nbsp;damage.</p>",
